<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201028/2bb518978fd64de1a65c60d24c4aa0a4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>2、直腿硬拉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201028/099a004b9fba46e3a2fbb4b50a011dbc.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>3、高位向下划船</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201028/c3f0933493f8473fa8df9c92b35aeafd.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
